data.description: Everything you need right where you need it!  Near EAFB, Beaches, NWFSC, shopping, hospitals and schools.  Great for your family or rental home...and NO HOA!  3 bedrooms, 2 full baths upstairs and 1/2 bath downstairs, lots of closets, 2 pantries in the kitchen with a new garbage disposal and refrigerator that is less than 2 yrs old. A/C recently serviced and refurbished. A back patio and upstairs patio provide expanded living spaces to enjoy.  Laundry room off the back patio offers convenience and the washer & dryer stay with the house.  A garage with work space, you're all set!  To see this fine, functional, pet friendly home with a fenced back yard, call your Realtor today!
